Output Projection Layer (LM Head)
│
├── 1. Input Hidden State
│     ├── Tensor from Final LayerNorm
│     └── Shape: (batch_size × seq_len × hidden_dim)
│
├── 2. Optional Hidden State Processing
│     ├── Dropout (optional)
│     └── Hidden state reshaping
│
├── 3. Linear Projection
│     │
│     ├── Weight Matrix
│     │      ├── Shape: (hidden_dim × vocab_size)
│     │      └── Trainable parameters
│     │
│     ├── Bias Vector
│     │      ├── Shape: (vocab_size)
│     │      └── Optional in some models
│     │
│     └── Matrix Multiplication
│            └── hidden_state × W + b
│
├── 4. Weight Tying (optional but common)
│     ├── Share weights with token embedding matrix
│     └── Reduces parameter count
│
├── 5. Vocabulary Logits
│     ├── Output tensor
│     └── Shape: (batch_size × seq_len × vocab_size)
│
├── 6. Logit Scaling / Temperature Adjustment (optional)
│     └── logits / temperature
│
└── 7. Output Interface
      ├── Passed to Softmax layer
      └── Used for next-token prediction